The valkyrie smiled and grabbed a napkin.  She wipes the few drops of formula from Elita's face.  She mixes another batch, bottles it, and also opens one of the baby food jars.  She set them in front of the baby.
"You can have either one.  Or both, if you want." 

airly2000 <airly2002@...> wrote:
Elita:

Elita stopped to sob and with her both little arms took her bottle and started to drink her meal. She drank quick due her hunger while a little drop of Baby formula was falling from her cheeks.

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, "The Ultimate Archfiend of Darkness, Devouring" <bustercross365@y...> wrote:
Organics:
 
Organics tried to sooth the baby, but to no avail.  She then began to search the mess hall for anything the baby might eat.  She found a few bottles and formula.  She also found jarred baby food, in case she didn't want the bottle.  She gathered it all up and brought it to the table.  She made up the formula and poured it into a bottle.  
she then presented it to Elita, hopeful it would please her.
"Here you go, a bottle, just as you asked, I hope."
